(1195, 169, 'news_content', 'Brownlee would like to welcome 2 new associates to their legal team\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Cecilia V. Hoover</strong>\r\nThe Partnership welcomes Cecilia V. Hoover to the Litigation and Insurance Defence Team in their Calgary Office. Cecilia received her law degree from the Osgoode Hall Law School in 2002 and is a member of both the Alberta and Ontario Bar. You can view Cecilia''s complete <a href="http://brownleelaw.com/calgary-lawyers?sobi2Task=sobi2Details&amp;catid=36&amp;sobi2Id=107">biography here.</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Aaron K.A. Peterkin</strong>\r\nAaron K.A. Peterkin is welcomed by Brownlee LLP as part of their Litigation and Insurance Defence Team in their Edmonton Office. Aaron received his Law Degree from the University of Edinburgh and his Masters in Commercial Law at the University of Nottingham. Aaron is a member of both the Alberta and Ontario Bar. You can view Aaron''s complete <a href="http://brownleelaw.com/edmonton?sobi2Task=sobi2Details&amp;catid=35&amp;sobi2Id=108">biography here.</a>'),
