(1210, 171, 'news_content', 'All AAMDC convention delegates are welcome to attend the Brownlee LLP St. Patty''s Day Celebration!\r\n\r\nIn conjunction with the AAMDC 2014 spring convention the Partners of Brownlee LLP invite all convention delegates to attend our St. Patrick''s Day as follows!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nMonday March, 17th 2014\r\n\r\nThe Westin Edmonon - Devonian Room\r\n\r\n6:00PM'),
