(25, 1, '2014-02-28 20:11:23', '2014-02-28 20:11:23', 'Brownlee supports various local, regional, and national charities on an ongoing basis through sponsorships and donations; however our biggest collaboration is that of our fall United Way Campaign. Brownlee supports this cause annually and in 2013 made a total contribution of $60,177.50, our biggest single contribution yet! Our total funds raised are now at an astounding $512,800.50.', 'Community Involvement', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'community-involvement', '', '', '2014-02-28 20:22:57', '2014-02-28 20:22:57', '', 9, 'http://localhost/brownlee/?page_id=25', 0, 'page', '', 0),
